OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FThe fine
OL,6,Fweather will continue this evening and
OL,7,Fovernight, with sunny spells to end
OL,8,Fthe day, followed by clear periods and
OL,9,Flight winds overnight. Patchy mist or
OL,10,Ffog may develop along with a frost in
OL,11,Frural areas.
OL,12,
OL,13,CMonday:FThere will be some sunshine on
OL,14,FMonday, though patchy cloudy likely at
OL,15,Ftimes. A slight easterly breeze
OL,16,Fdeveloping, though feeling pleasant
OL,17,Fenough in any lingering brighter
OL,18,Fbreaks.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
