OL,5,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:FDry
OL,6,Fand bright through much of the outlook
OL,7,Fperiod with some patchy cloud around
OL,8,Fat times. A strong and gusty wind
OL,9,Fdeveloping for a time later Tuesday
OL,10,Fand through Wednesday.
